'''諾姆·麥克唐納'''（'''{{lang-en|Norman Gene Macdonald}}'''，{{bd|1959年|10月17日|2021年|9月14日|catIdx=MacDonald}}）<ref>The capitalization of Norm Macdonald's surname has been inconsistently reported in publications such as ''TVGuide'', but books discussing Norm such as Shales (2003) and [http://books.google.com/books?id=hAdZIuU0wFgC&pg=PA60&dq=norm+macdonald&hl=en&ei=KtvcTdDWFomosQPcvI2SBw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&ved=0CEoQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=norm%20macdonald&f=false Crawford] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=hAdZIuU0wFgC&pg=PA60&dq=norm+macdonald&hl=en&ei=KtvcTdDWFomosQPcvI2SBw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&ved=0CEoQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q=norm%20macdonald&f=false |date=20140112034034 }} (2000), the Game Show Network, and Comedy Central ''[[Sports_Show_with_Norm_Macdonald|Sports Show with Norm Macdonald]]'' and comedy CD all consistently report "Macdonald" (lowercase "d") as his surname.</ref><ref name="TVGuide">{{cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/norm-macdonald168320 |title=Norm Macdonald biography |publisher=[[TV_Guide|TVGuide.com]] |accessdate=11 December 2015 |archivedate=2015-12-11 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6dhR8i4tQ?url=http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/norm-macdonald/168320 |deadurl=no }}</ref>是[[加拿大|加拿大]]的一位演員、作家、製作人和喜劇人。他曾是[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]五季的固定來賓，並且曾主持了三年的Weekend Update。在1999年至2001年，他曾創建了諾姆秀（The Norm Show），他也被喜劇中心評為最偉大的100名喜劇演員第83位。
諾姆在2021年9月14日因癌症過世。<ref>https://www.npr.org/2021/09/14/1037069333/norm-macdonald-dead-snl-comedian</ref>

